rules.fixed_sql:
SELECT icu.SUBJECT_ID, icu.HADM_ID
FROM ICUSTAYS icu
JOIN LABEVENTS lab ON icu.SUBJECT_ID = lab.SUBJECT_ID AND icu.HADM_ID = lab.HADM_ID
JOIN D_LABITEMS dlab ON lab.ITEMID = dlab.ITEMID
WHERE dlab.LABEL = 'Phosphate'
  AND lab.CHARTTIME BETWEEN icu.INTIME AND icu.INTIME + INTERVAL '24' HOUR
  AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM LABEVENTS lab2
    WHERE lab2.SUBJECT_ID = icu.SUBJECT_ID
      AND lab2.HADM_ID = icu.HADM_ID
      AND lab2.ITEMID = lab.ITEMID
      AND lab2.CHARTTIME BETWEEN icu.INTIME AND icu.INTIME + INTERVAL '24' HOUR
    GROUP BY TRUNC((CAST(lab2.CHARTTIME AS DATE) - CAST(icu.INTIME AS DATE)) * 24 / 6)
    HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT TRUNC((CAST(lab2.CHARTTIME AS DATE) - CAST(icu.INTIME AS DATE)) * 24 / 6)) >= 4
  )
  AND ROWNUM = 1

rules.fixed_sql: SELECT CASE WHEN p.ANCHOR_AGE < 18 THEN '0-17' WHEN p.ANCHOR_AGE BETWEEN 18 AND 34 THEN '18-34' WHEN p.ANCHOR_AGE BETWEEN 35 AND 49 THEN '35-49' WHEN p.ANCHOR_AGE BETWEEN 50 AND 64 THEN '50-64' ELSE '65+' END AS age_group, COUNT(DISTINCT ic.HADM_ID) AS patient_count FROM ICUSTAYS ic JOIN ADMISSIONS a ON ic.HADM_ID = a.HADM_ID JOIN DIAGNOSES_ICD d ON a.HADM_ID = d.HADM_ID JOIN D_ICD_DIAGNOSES diag ON d.ICD_CODE = diag.ICD_CODE AND d.ICD_VERSION = diag.ICD_VERSION JOIN PATIENTS p ON a.SUBJECT_ID = p.SUBJECT_ID WHERE diag.LONG_TITLE LIKE '%sepsis%' AND ic.LOS > 2 AND ic.HADM_ID IS NOT NULL GROUP BY CASE WHEN p.ANCHOR_AGE < 18 THEN '0-17' WHEN p.ANCHOR_AGE BETWEEN 18 AND 34 THEN '18-34' WHEN p.ANCHOR_AGE BETWEEN 35 AND 49 THEN '35-49' WHEN p.ANCHOR_AGE BETWEEN 50 AND 64 THEN '50-64' ELSE '65+' END
